Whether rescuing a kitten or saving a train from a rockslide, the PAW Patrol is always up for the challenge while also making sure there’s time for a game or a laugh.

Episodes.Intro: A kitten named Precious is floating out to sea, and the PAW Patrol must rescue her, but that’s not all. The PAW Patrol must also act fast to find her owner before the mischievous kitten gets into big trouble.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 1x1

Episodes.Intro: On a snow and icy day, Mr. Porter’s van ends up sliding on ice. If the ice cracks, it will fall into the bottom of the bay, and inside of the truck has all the pups’ treats and food in it!
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 1x10

Episodes.Intro: The PAW Patrol are having a great time at the Adventure Bay Hoedown, but trouble starts to brew when Farmer Al’s cows get spooked out and are on the loose in Adventure Bay.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 1x11

Episodes.Intro: A Halloween party turns into a spooky time when there’s a ghostly figure roaming around on a ship. Can the PAW Patrol solve the paranormal mystery and save the Halloween party?
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 1x12

Episodes.Intro: It’s Alex’s first day of school, but he has lost his backpack! So the PAW Patrol agrees to help him find it.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 1x13

Episodes.Intro: It’s a hot day and the pups head for the water park, but the pool is empty! The water tower that pumps water into the pool is tilted and has a bent pipe.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 1x14

Episodes.Intro: Cap’n Turbot got The Flounder stuck on some rocks. If the PAW Patrol doesn’t save him, The Flounder will sink to the bottom of the bay!
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 1x15

Episodes.Intro: Santa’s sleigh crashes and breaks in a snowstorm on Christmas Eve, and all of the presents are scattered across Adventure Bay. It’s up to the PAW Patrol to fix the sleigh, round up the reindeer, find the presents, find the magic star, and most of all, save Christmas for Adventure Bay.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 1x16

Episodes.Intro: Ryder and the PAW Patrol need to rescue Alex on Jakes mountain./The pups find strange footprints in the snow on the mountain outside Adventure Bay. Everyone thinks it’s a “snow monster” and it’s scaring the skiers away.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 1x17

Episodes.Intro: When Ryder’s Robot Pup breaks and starts going wild around Adventure Bay, it takes the whole Paw Patrol to help Ryder find it.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 1x18

Episodes.Intro: An escaped baby monkey named Mandy leads the PAW Patrol on a chase through Adventure Bay, when she steals Mr. Porter van full of bananas.Chase befriends a baby owl and with the PAW Patrol helps rescue its mother who is trapped in the knothole of a fallen tree.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 1x19

Episodes.Intro: A train car falls off the tracks and also breaks some rails. A train is coming later with important packages in it, with the all new Pup Pup Boogie 2.0 dance game. The PAW Patrol tries to fix the tracks, but how will they fix the tracks when Rubble sprains his paw and can’t work? Can Chase save the day?
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 1x2

Episodes.Intro: A baby Bat decides to take a nap hanging from the Town Hall’s bell and Mayor Goodway can’t ring it. Ryder and the Pups attempt to rescue the bat quietly so it doesn’t wake up, but it does and causes trouble around town. It’s up to Ryder and the Pups to get the Bat and return her to her Bat cave. Alex is afraid to go to the dentist, so Chase and the PAW Patrol work together to show Alex that fears can be overcome.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 1x20

Episodes.Intro: It’s Adventure Bay’s annual Easter Egg Hunt and the pups are helping Mayor Goodway with the egg decorating. The hunt for a very special egg leads Ryder and the PAW Patrol on an exciting adventure.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 1x21

Episodes.Intro: Cap’n Turbot has accidentally locked himself inside the lighthouse, so it is up to the pups to rescue a rowboat drifting out to sea.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 1x22

Episodes.Intro: It’s Adventure Bay Race Day and the pups are about to race each other all across the town to see who is the fastest pup. One other competitor unexpectedly shows up though, Alex in his super trike! Mr.Porter enters a cake competition and needs Ryder and the pups to help him bake the biggest and tastiest cake. The race is on to get their cake baked and to the competition on time!
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 1x23

Episodes.Intro: Rubble has a wondrous dream, similar to Jack and the Beanstalk, where Marshall grows a giant beanstalk and Alex is a giant. However, when giant Alex starts to cause havoc, Ryder and the PAW Patrol must keep him occupied. When Cap’n Turbot needs to get a picture of the rare Blue Footed Booby Bird when his French cousin, Francois Turbot, decides to help but gets caught on a cliff! It’s up to the PAW Patrol to rescue him and bring the two cousins together again.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 1x24

Episodes.Intro: When Chickaletta falls in a cave in the ground it’s up to the PAW Patrol to save her! Tons of baby turtles are popping up all over the town. Can the PAW Patrol help get them back to their homes before they get hurt?
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 1x25

Episodes.Intro: Cap’n Turbot accidentally stumbles into a secret cavern that was once a pirate’s hideout. When the PAW Patrol rescues him, they find an incomplete treasure map. The adventure is on as the pups follow clues to find the missing map pieces, and eventually to an amazing sunken pirate treasure!
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 1x26

Episodes.Intro: Baby sea turtles were hatching at the other side of the road near the beach. They can’t get to the beach without crossing the street, there are cars, skateboarders, scooters and all the hungry naughty seagulls around, not to mention Alex’s rambunctious antics.

Episodes.Intro: Ellie, the baby elephant from the Circus train, has escaped and is loose in Adventure Bay!

Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 1x5

Episodes.Intro: The pups help a young boy named Alex fix his broken tricycle and teach him a valuable lesson of taking new things slow.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 1x6

Episodes.Intro: A bunch of adorable bunnies have come to Farmer Yumi’s carrot patch. The PAW Patrol must catch them all and relocate them to a perfect new home.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 1x7

Episodes.Intro: There’s an oil spill in the bay, and a Baby Whale swam into the oil. The PAW Patrol must clean up the Baby Whale and the oil spill before more animals living in Adventure Bay are harmed by it.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 1x8

Episodes.Intro: This episode is a flashback story of how Rubble joined the PAW Patrol. Rubble must help Jake when he gets trapped in an Avalanche.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 1x9

Episodes.Intro: The pups must find a way to get a group of penguins back to the South Pole.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 2x1

Episodes.Intro: Ryder and the Pups head out for a day of Parachute training, but Marshall decides to stay back because of his fear of heights.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 2x11

Episodes.Intro: Feeling like his clumsy ways are constantly messing up his friends’ fun, Marshall decides to take a break from the PAW Patrol and goes off into the woods. Once the pups notice Marshall is gone, they jump to action to find him and bring him back to the Lookout.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 2x12

Episodes.Intro: Ryder and the PAW Patrol head to the Jungle in the PAW PATROLLER to help their good friend CARLOS find his lost Parrot, Matea!
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 2x13

Episodes.Intro: Mayor Goodway has her hands full with her twin niece and nephew Julia and Julius. She calls on the PAW Patrol to rescue them from a tree, and then twin sit for the day!
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 2x14

Episodes.Intro: The Pups are on a PAW Patroller road trip to the Savana where they meet up with Photo Safari fans Cap’n Turbot and his cousin François Turbot. In the middle of the night the campers are awakened by an intruder who turns out to be a lost baby elephant – Gilda.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 2x15

Episodes.Intro: When the Pups and Cap’n Turbot camp out under the very rare Magical Mer Moon, magical things begin to happen. Lured by the mystical Mer pup song and then transformed into Mer pups themselves, Skye and Zuma and even water resistant Rocky perform an underwater rescue in a sunken old ship. Cap’n Turbot and Ryder help out by diving deep to bottom of the Bay in their Diving Bell to help a Mer Mom and pup.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 2x16

Episodes.Intro: The PAW Patrol is just about to zoom off on their latest rescue to help Farmer Al capture his run-a-way pigs, Emma and Corny, when Chase sneezes, then Zuma sneezes and in a blink of an eye, Skye joins the group of sick puppies.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 2x17

Episodes.Intro: Alex is working towards getting his Action Scouts Fire Safety Badge, and who better to help him learn all about Fire Safety than Marshall and the PAW Patrol!

Episodes.Intro: It’s the annual Mayor’s Race and Mayor Goodway is determined to give it her best.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 2x19

Episodes.Intro: An alien lands on Earth at Farmer Yumi’s place, and the gang try to repair his spaceship so he can return home.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 2x2

Episodes.Intro: The PAW Patrol must come to the rescue when Wally’s special friend, Walinda, gets tangled in an anchor chain; Cap’n Turbot and his cousin are in the middle of an archaeological dig when the cliff they are on collapses all around them.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 2x20

Episodes.Intro: Cap’n Turbot and his cousin Francois are watching white whales in Adventure Bay when their boat hits a rock and starts to sink; the PAW Patrol must track down some loose penguins and help them return to the land of ice and snow.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 2x21

Episodes.Intro: While Sensei Yumi teaches all the Pups the ancient art of Pup-Fu, Mayor Humdinger steals an ancient scroll that holds all the secrets of the art.

Episodes.Intro: Jake and Everest are excited today’s the day of the big Snowboard Competition, until they look outside and see the course is completely buried under blanket of snow; The Cap’n is about to test it out in an underwater adventure when Chickaletta, Cali and a seagull beat him to it. All the animal activity on the control panel drives the diving bell to the bottom of the bay.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 2x23

Episodes.Intro: While delivering special pizza dough for a party, Alex and Mr. Porter get into an accident; a storm causes Skye to crash land in the snow while on her way to Jake’s Mountain.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 2x24

Episodes.Intro: When a storm blows through the town right before a concert, the pups must work together to clean up the mess; Mayor Goodway’s backpack slips down the side of a cliff with Chickaletta in it.

Episodes.Intro: The PAW Patrol must rescue Jake when his ankle gets stuck between some fallen rocks.

Episodes.Intro: An Arctic storm picks up, but Jake finds help from a brave mountain ranger pup named Everest!
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 2x6

Episodes.Intro: The PAW Patrol heads to the Jungle in the PAW Patroller to meet Ryder’s 10 year old pen-pal, Carlos.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 2x7

Episodes.Intro: A wintertime storm causes trouble all over Adventure Bay.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 2x8

Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 2x9

Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 3x1

Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 3x10

Episodes.Intro: While on a trip to the Arctic, Cap’n Turbot needs the pups’ help to get a family of polar bears back together. Marshall puts on a sheep costume to find missing lambs on a farm.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 3x11

Episodes.Intro: Rocky uses his tools to repair the tires on a school bus. Rocky uses his tools to repair the tires on a school bus.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 3x12

Episodes.Intro: The pups set out to recover a missing robotic dinosaur. The pups have trouble filming their entry for a film festival.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 3x14

Episodes.Intro: The PAW Patrol’s newest member, Tracker, helps find an ancient crown.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 3x15

Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 3x16

Episodes.Intro: The pups compete against a team of monkeys as part of a charity kickball game.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 3x17

Episodes.Intro: The pups take care of an ant infestation on the day of Adventure Bay’s jam festival. Zuma tracks down a pig on a windsurfing board.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 3x18

Episodes.Intro: The pups must stop overgrown tomatoes from rolling around Adventure Bay. Marshall is beamed into the sky by space aliens.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 3x19

Episodes.Intro: The pups search for gold using Rocky’s makeshift sifting tools. The pups take a break from washing the PAW Patroller. When they return, the PAW Patroller is missing.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 3x2

Episodes.Intro: The pups’ hunt for berries is cut short when Everest is sprayed by a skunk. During a whale watching trip, Cap’n Turbot finds a baby whale trapped under an ice sheet.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 3x20

Episodes.Intro: Rocky loses his voice while visiting Tracker in the jungle, so a talkative parrot helps him fulfill his PAW Patrol duties. Episodes.Intro: Tracker helps out when the pups need to find Cap’n Turbot’s skating penguins, who have gone missing during a blizzard.

Episodes.Intro: Cap’n Turbot and Francois break their hang glider while doing research on albino monkeys.

Episodes.Intro: Tracker’s new Venus flytrap grows at an unexpected rate after being planted in an unsuitable area.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 3x24

Episodes.Intro: The PAW Patrol must find a way to save their waterlogged 18-wheeler after it sinks to the bottom of Adventure Bay.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 3x25

Episodes.Intro: A “floating ray” from outer space causes the people of Adventure Bay to float in mid-air.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 3x26

Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 3x3

Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 3x4

Episodes.Intro: Cap’n Turbot and Francois go on a monkey communication expedition, but are put in danger when the volcano on the island erupts. The PAW Patrol uses their new Air Patroller to rescue the two, along with a family of monkeys.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 3x5

Episodes.Intro: Rubble dreams about saving his idol, Apollo the Super-Pup, from an evil Spider King.
Episodes.Name: Paw Patrol 3x7

Episodes.Intro: Capn’ Turbot’s weather blimp is taken by Mayor Humdinger, who plans to use it to change the weather in Foggy Bottom.

Episodes.Intro: Cap’n Turbot’s boat, the Flounder, is sunk by a large pink octopus.

Episodes.Intro: A giant monkey follows the PAW Patrol home after a trip to the jungle.

Intro: David Attenborough presents a documentary series exploring how animals meet the challenges of surviving in the most iconic habitats on earth.

Episodes.Intro: Islands are wildlife sanctuaries, but surviving in isolation comes with extreme challenges.
Episodes.Name: Planet Earth II 1x1

Episodes.Intro: The great mountain ranges are some of the planet’s most spectacular landscapes, but they are unforgiving places to live in, and only a few animals have what it takes to live at extreme altitude. Mountain animals are amongst the most elusive in the world, and this film provides unique and intimate glimpses into their secretive lives. Witness the moment four snow leopards come together when a mother and cub become trapped between two rival males. Join grizzly bears as they dance against trees to rub off their winter fur and soar with golden eagles hunting amongst Europe’s snow-capped peaks.
Episodes.Name: Planet Earth II 1x2

Episodes.Intro: A look at the animals competing to survive in the rich habitats of the planet’s jungles.
Episodes.Name: Planet Earth II 1x3

Episodes.Intro: The world’s deserts force animals to come up with ingenious ways of coping with hostile conditions, giving rise to the most incredible survival stories on earth.
Episodes.Name: Planet Earth II 1x4

Episodes.Intro: Grasslands cover one quarter of all land and support the greatest gatherings of wildlife on Earth. The extraordinary creatures that live here must survive the most hostile seasons on the planet. From bizarre looking Saiga antelope in Asia, rarely seen by humans, to the giant ant-eaters of Brazil, grassland animals show remarkable survival techniques. In the flooded Okavango, lions take on formidable buffalo in epic battles, stunning bee-eaters ride on the back of ostriches like miniature jockeys, while caribou embark on great migrations, where they must cross paths with their nemesis, Arctic wolves.
Episodes.Name: Planet Earth II 1x5

Episodes.Intro: Cities are growing at a faster rate than any other habitat on Earth. They may seem an unlikely place for animals to thrive, but for the bold this is a world of surprising opportunity. Leopards prowl the streets of Mumbai, peregrine falcons hunt amongst New York’s skyscrapers and a million starlings perform spectacular aerial dances over Rome. We welcome some creatures into our cities; in Jodhpur langurs are revered as religious deities and in Harar locals live in harmony with wild hyenas. Many animals, however, are struggling to cope in the urban jungle. As the architects of this environment will we choose to build cities that create a home for both us and for wildlife?
Episodes.Name: Planet Earth II 1x6

Name: Planet Earth II

Intro: Cuộc phiêu lưu gia đình hoạt hình dựa trên một câu chuyện có thật kể về câu chuyện ấm áp, sắp đến tuổi của một người đàn ông và người bạn thân nhất của anh ta, một chú chó đáng yêu và không biết sợ tên là Jock. Lấy bối cảnh ở Bushveld gần công viên quốc gia Kruger nổi tiếng thế giới ngày nay, câu chuyện gia đình hoạt hình này kể về cuộc phiêu lưu của Jock với Fritz, chủ nhân của anh. Jock thoát khỏi cái chết, xây dựng tình bạn điên rồ và thể hiện lòng trung thành vô song của mình với Fritz. Câu chuyện lấy bối cảnh vào cuối những năm 1880 khi sự giàu có về khoáng sản của châu Phi, đời sống động vật và vẻ đẹp tự nhiên không gì sánh được đã thu hút và làm say mê các nhà thám hiểm và nhà thám hiểm từ khắp nơi trên thế giới. Một nơi mà trò chơi lớn lang thang trong hàng ngàn người và những câu chuyện hoang dã nhất là có thật! Jock Of The Bushveld là một câu chuyện tuyệt vời và là loài động vật kinh điển duy nhất ra khỏi châu Phi.
Name: Jock of the Bushveld

Name: Barbie in A Mermaid Tale

In this exciting sea-quel, Merliah makes a splash when she heads to Australia for the ultimate surfing competition. When the evil mermaid Eris escapes from her whirlpool with plans to take over the throne of Oceana, Merliah and her sea friends dive in to stop her. It’s a fresh new adventure where Merliah learns that anything is possible and she really can have the best of both worlds!
Name: Barbie in A Mermaid Tale 2

Intro: Barbie is Kara – a modern-day princess with a normal life. Kissed by a butterfly which gives her superpowers and allows her to become a Super Sparkle, she is ready to save the kingdom from evil – were it not for her jealous cousin who is also kissed by the butterfly and becomes her rival and nemesis. Watch as Super Sparkle and Dark Sparkle learn that together they can become a great team for good once they learn the power of friendship.
Name: Barbie in Princess Power

Intro: In this upbeat musical, Barbie stars as Princess Courtney, a modern princess whose world is turned upside down when she switches places with Erika, a famous rockstar. Two very different worlds collide when a mix-up sends Princess Courtney to Camp Pop and Erika, to Camp Royalty. While the leaders of the rival camps try to correct the mix-up, both Courtney and Erika learn to adjust to the different worlds and have fun while making new, unexpected friends. When the girls learn both camps are at risk of shutting down, they must embrace their differences, find their true voices, and come together for an epic sing-off that shows anything is possible when you dare to dream big!
Name: Barbie in Rock 'N Royals

While Mariposa doesn’t make a great first impression on the King, she becomes fast friends with his shy daughter, Princess Catania. Episodes.Intro: A horde of pixies descends on Arcadia Oaks High, sending the student body into a tailspin. Angor Rot comes to Jim with a surprising proposal.
Episodes.Name: Trollhunters 1x20

Episodes.Intro: The Changeling posing as Claire’s little brother throws a house party for the trolls of Arcadia. Jim and Toby look for a way to take Strickler’s ring.
Episodes.Name: Trollhunters 1x21

Episodes.Intro: Every second counts when Jim turns to a time-stopping Kairosect to snatch Strickler’s ring, save his mother and find the second Triumbric Stone.
Episodes.Name: Trollhunters 1x22

Episodes.Intro: A troll queen arrives from afar to take AAARRRGGHH!!! back to his homeland, revealing his devastating secret. Strickler asks Jim for protection.
Episodes.Name: Trollhunters 1x23

Episodes.Intro: A reluctant Jim joins forces with Strickler to keep Barbara alive. Gnome Chompsky returns from the Darklands with important news about Enrique.
Episodes.Name: Trollhunters 1x24

Episodes.Intro: With Barbara’s life hanging in the balance, Jim races to break the spell that bonds her to Strickler. Angor Rot attacks Toby and Claire.
Episodes.Name: Trollhunters 1x25

Episodes.Intro: The heroes brace for Angor Rot’s inevitable invasion and prepare for the fight of their lives. Jim locates the last Triumbric Stone.
Episodes.Name: Trollhunters 1x26

Episodes.Intro: Jim and Toby tour Heartstone Trollmarket, where Jim begins his training and the presence of the first human Trollhunter stirs up bitter resentment.
Episodes.Name: Trollhunters 1x3

Episodes.Intro: While Jim gets a crash course in troll history, big problems — and a bully — await him in the human world. What better time for his first mission?
Episodes.Name: Trollhunters 1x4

Episodes.Intro: Jim tries to get closer to Claire on a school field trip to the museum, only to learn that the museum’s curator, Ms. Nomura, has an unsettling secret.
Episodes.Name: Trollhunters 1x5

Episodes.Intro: Jim preps for a high-stakes rematch against Draal, the amulet’s seemingly rightful heir. But their animosity gives way to a surprising partnership.
Episodes.Name: Trollhunters 1x6

Episodes.Intro: Armed with an ancient troll-hunting tool, Jim and Toby set out to unmask the Changelings living among them. Claire makes Jim a tempting offer.
Episodes.Name: Trollhunters 1x7

Episodes.Intro: While Draal settles into his new digs, Jim volunteers to babysit so he can find out whether Claire’s little brother, Enrique, is a Changeling.
Episodes.Name: Trollhunters 1x8

Episodes.Intro: Jim’s 16th birthday is full of surprises, including the arrival of a terrifying new species of troll that’s immune to the effects of sunlight.
Episodes.Name: Trollhunters 1x9

Name: Trollhunters

Intro: Hugo is an orphan boy living in the walls of a train station in 1930s Paris. He learned to fix clocks and other gadgets from his father and uncle which he puts to use keeping the train station clocks running. The only thing that he has left that connects him to his dead father is an automaton (mechanical man) that doesn’t work without a special key which Hugo needs to find to unlock the secret he believes it contains. On his adventures, he meets with a shopkeeper, George Melies, who works in the train station and his adventure-seeking god-daughter. Hugo finds that they have a surprising connection to his father and the automaton, and he discovers it unlocks some memories the old man has buried inside regarding his past.
Name: Hugo

Intro: Paulie, an intelligent parrot who actually talks, relates the story of his struggle to a Russian immigrant who works as a janitor at the research institute where he is housed and neglected. Paulie’s story begins many years earlier when he is given as a gift to a little girl who stutters. Eventually, he teaches the girl to speak correctly but is taken away by her father because he believes the girl cannot distinguish fantasy from reality because she believes the bird can talk. Paulie goes through a series of adventures with a pawn shop owner, an aging widow, a Mexican-American troubadour and a would be thief before being taken to the institute where he now lives
Name: Paulie

Intro: A husband (Isao Hashizume) and wife (Kazuko Yoshiyuki) have been married for 50 years. For her birthday, the husband asks the wife what she wants for her birthday present. She replies that she wants a divorce. The wife’s divorce announcement sends the entire family into chaos.
Name: What a Wonderful Family!

However, when one of 600 million children to receive a gift from Santa on Christmas Eve is missed, it is deemed ‘acceptable’ to all but one – Arthur. Arthur Claus is Santa’s misfit son who executes an unauthorized rookie mission to get the last present half way around the globe before dawn on Christmas morning.

Intro: Dumbo is a baby elephant born with oversized ears and a supreme lack of confidence. But thanks to his even more diminutive buddy — Timothy the Mouse — the pint-sized pachyderm learns to surmount all obstacles.
Name: Dumbo

Intro: London high-society mouse, Roddy is flushed down the toilet by Sid, a common sewer rat. Hang on for a madcap adventure deep in the sewer bowels of Ratropolis, where Roddy meets the resourceful Rita, the rodent-hating Toad and his faithful thugs, Spike and Whitey.
Name: Flushed Away

Intro: As the son of a Viking leader on the cusp of manhood, shy Hiccup Horrendous Haddock III faces a rite of passage: he must kill a dragon to prove his warrior mettle. But after downing a feared dragon, he realizes that he no longer wants to destroy it, and instead befriends the beast – which he names Toothless – much to the chagrin of his warrior father
Name: How to Train Your Dragon

Intro: One day, Horton the elephant hears a cry from help coming from a speck of dust. Even though he can’t see anyone on the speck, he decides to help it. As it turns out, the speck of dust is home to the Whos, who live in their city of Whoville. Horton agrees to help protect the Whos and their home
Name: Horton Hears a Who!
